name: Sweet Sour Source
body:
### Ingredients

* 2 interested developers

* 1 daring challenge

* 1 cup of extraordinary ideas

* pinch 	sugar

* just enough spare time

### Directions

Wash and mix ideas thoroughly and them combine them with rest of ingredients. Let it cook for some time and stir regularly.

Top with sugar and serve immediately.
